        "content": {
          "excerpt_text": "Incident began at 2026-02-27 04:36 and ended at 2026-02-27 06:45 (all times are US/Pacific ). Preliminary Incident Report We apologize for the inconvenience this service disruption may have caused. We would like to provide some information about this incident below. Please note, this information is based on our best knowledge at the time of posting and is subject to change as our investigation continues. A final Incident Report with preventative actions will be posted once our investigation...",
