        "updated_at": "2026-03-04T23:23:18Z",
        "headline": "UPDATE: Vertex AI Gemini API customers experienced increased error rates when accessing the global endpoint",
        "content": {
          "excerpt_text": "Incident began at 2026-02-27 04:36 and ended at 2026-02-27 06:45 (all times are US/Pacific ). Description Between Friday, 2026-02-27, 04:36 and 06:45 PST, customers experienced increased error rates when accessing the Vertex Gemini API Global endpoint. The issue impacted API requests to multiple Gemini models. The incident also caused downstream impact to Dialogflow CX, Agent Assist, Google Cloud Support AI agent, and Customer Experience Agent Studio, which rely on Gemini APIs. Preliminary...",
          "lang": "en"
        },
        "provenance": {
          "fetched_at": "2026-03-04T23:49:01Z",
